Hard drivers are more importent than any thing else. Rack is nothing but a contrainer it hold no.of hard drives. 

Between operating system and RACK there will be a network switch to access the data from RACK. If the operating system failes automatically it switch to other operating systems. 

If you external user want to access you data form RACK. There is a separate machine (Fireall and Separate switch) to access data...it will not allow directly hit to machine. (Writting swith (Private) and Accessing switch is different(Public)).


